summary: My first mod. Adds a craft-able, hone-able, and enchant-able Executioner Axe that has improved stats.
descriptionHtml:
My first mod. Adds a craft-able Executioner Axe that has improved stats and is one-handed. Figured out what was causing the display problem. it equips as 1 handed but has to be swung as 2 handed. Hope you enjoy it and have fun. Still working on improving it and learning in the process. Please endorse.
Thanks and enjoy.
author: corrupted78
